                  <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='12'>Key Insights:</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='12'>- USA leads all countries in total order volume.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='12'>- Côte de Blaye dominates product revenue at $53.2M — double its nearest competitor.</run>
